    "body": "Well, as I said, I didn't see any warnings. I'm all for deprecating and removing things, but you have to make your deprecations actually seen. Otherwise, it's a waste of time.\n\nFor SymPy, we have a special `SymPyDeprecationWarning` subclass of `DeprecationWarning`, which we enable always. \n"
