    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@asmeurer I hear you, but that's unreasonable to ask from all the users that are not developpers, and assuming you want to enable it for sympy then `filterwarnings('default', '.*', DeprecationWarning, module='sympy.*')` will enable that for all your user, and only at Sympy level, so you will be warned if sympy uses deprecated feature, regardless of whether it's from IPython or another package. \n"
